    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Partners in wedded or parental relations, most often applicable when the person holds certain titles, such as Queen-Consort, the wife of a king, or King-Consort, Prince-Consort, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
